<L>__{exterior interior kitchen yard. day.}
<A>__{albert runs out. he rushes into the kitchen. his mother stares out the window. she has been crying.}
<C>__{albert}
<D>__{what has he done with him?}
<A>__{she says nothing, but her face gives everything away. albert in a panic turns and runs out into the lane. mrs. narracott tears up again.}
